        Template
        ========
        
        Static methods to wrap text in ANSI Colours.
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install by running:
        
        .. code:: python
        
            pip install ansi_colours
        
        ::
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
        
            from ansi_colours import AnsiColours as colour
        
            # Red text
        
            colour.red("I'm red")
        
        ::
        
